input.new_string:
An ark comprises the
{rbtga_ark_image}
(`-image` suffix) containing the container image and the
{rbtga_ark_about}
(`-about` suffix) containing build provenance and metadata.
Optionally, an ark includes the
{rbtga_ark_vouch}
(`-vouch` suffix) recording verified SLSA provenance facts.
